pageContext.claim: “The large and violent French protests don't take into account how badly the United States has been treated on Trade by the European Union or on fair and reasonable payments for our GREAT military protection. Both of these topics must be remedied soon.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is creating a correlation that doesn't exist. The French protests have to do with French policy and there's no reason that French protestors would support policies that would be aligned with American interests.
